{"tid":1166104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟網上商店華為 MateBook X Pro 突被下架　封殺繼續擴展？","createTime":"2019-05-22T08:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T09:06:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0adc583a038d0ed3e3a34f1edc85530d6d64497e","tid":1166104,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"早前 Google 表示因為美國列華為公司到黑名單，將會停止對華為提供服務，包括 Google Play Store，及 Youtube 等，而現在戰線似乎進一步擴大，微軟的 Online Store上，華為的 MateBook X Pro 突然下架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Matebook-X-01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FMatebook-X-01.png&h=45880317&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMateBook X Pro下架目前微軟尚未有正式的回應，不過如果是因為黑名單問題，代表未來有機會連同 Windows 系統都不能在華為的電腦裝置上使用，將無法與 MacBook Pro等美國品牌競爭。<br />\n<br />\n早前美國宣佈對華為的禁令執行時間延遲 90 天，到 8 月才會執行，而現在 MateBook X Pro 下架一事，暫時未知道是否與禁令有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/05/22/matebookxpro/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F05%2F22%2Fmatebookxpro%2Fnotebook%2F&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=b8a31c58\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/05/22/matebookxpro/notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"3d1312c4281d6b080898f687e88e08421cc559c7","tid":1166104,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"另一個post日本都有鋪頭冇賣<br />\n未必係想封殺<br />\n而係部野都唔知做唔做到維修保養既情況下<br />\n大公司唔敢拎出嚟賣"},{"pid":"9095d708f1ec1b93691d7e46e0c0ca37b086c733","tid":1166104,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d1312c4281d6b080898f687e88e08421cc559c7","tid":1166104,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"另一個post日本都有鋪頭冇賣<br />\n未必係想封殺<br />\n而係部野都唔知做唔做到維修保養既情況下<br />\n大公司唔敢拎出嚟賣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"斷零件供應就無得維修保養<br />\n好正常，華為現在有料都留翻黎畀領導用"},{"p